social_posts.post_text:
Everyone please take the time to wish my beautiful girl a happy birthday!!! 🎊 
-
Madi is very humbled and often doesn’t talk about her accomplishments. My baby girl is making a name for herself at her workplace where she now is a  branch manager, she has made strives in her off season as a bodybuilder that she may not see, but I see each week. Her hard work and dedication always pays off as she works towards her goals and accomplishments. 23 has been a hell of a year for you, and I’ve been the man by your side to watch you succeed through it all. 
-
I am forever proud and grateful for you Madi. I love you, cheers to 24! 💕

It’s almost go time! ⏳
-
This off season has been the most productive off season yet. Excited is an understatement as we transition our way into prep for this 2023 season. I feel as if I have made great improvements since last year, and have the right coach and people in my corner to bring my best look. These snips from last years prep fire me up!
-
19 weeks 🔥
Coached by: @_cutz_ 🔪

11.5 weeks out. 💪🏽
-
Coach: @_cutz_

PREP UPDATE‼️
-
Change of plans this contest prep. @_cutz_ gave me the green light, and I am now 7 weeks out. I am enjoying the process, and have full trust and confidence within myself and my coach. Trying my best to be my best come show time. Time to execute! 💪🏽

7 weeks out. 💪🏽
-
Coach: @_cutz_ 🔪
Gym: @americasgymchicago

6.5 weeks out 💪🏽
-
Making posing a priority each day to perfect my craft. 
Coached by: @_cutz_ 🔪

5.6 weeks out today. Got a chance to check out @theshopgym out of town this weekend and figured I’d share a physique update! Time to get better.💪🏽 
-
Coach: @_cutz_ 🔪

5.5 out from show day. Doing my best to be at my best come that time…
-
For now, we work💪🏽
-
@_cutz_ 🔪

IT’S SHOW DAY BABY @madisen_dobbs ❤️
-
Everyone please take the time to wish my other half good luck today. I’ve watched this girl work for 20+ weeks, manage two banks, and deal with obstacles the average person wouldn’t know how to deal with in or out of prep. 
-
Being proud of you is an understatement, and watching you work makes me work even harder. It’s who you are and it’s what you do! I love you so much, and you motivate me and others and don’t even realize it. Now what do ya say it’s time to finish this damn thing!? 💪🏽

Post chest yesterday 💪🏽
-
4.5 weeks out and still a lot left in the tank. Time to push!
-
@_cutz_ 🔪

4 weeks out from @shreddedcheddarproductions brew city. 💪🏽
-
Time is flying by and changes are being made daily! I’m excited for this one but the work is far from over. Time to bring a better me 💪🏽

Pictures taken a few days ago post back day, but closing in on 3.5 weeks out.💪🏽
-
Not the best lighting in these, but there’s no fancy lighting on stage so here is a true representation of my current physique. Let’s finish this one strong!
-
Coach: @_cutz_ 🔪
@shreddedcheddarproductions

3 weeks out tomorrow‼️
-
Things are starting to click, just a tad bit left to strip off and we are there. 👌🏽 let’s land this plane and finish strong. 💪🏽
-
Coach: @_cutz_ 🔪

3 weeks out ⏳
-
A little flat today but giving full transparency with my physique. Unfortunately to get in condition you will have those days and it’s all apart of the process. This prep I have done my best by not getting ahead of myself and taking it day by day, meal by meal, training session to training session and I think it’s helped tremendously.
-
Job is far from finished and I have some work to do. So let’s work 💪🏽

2 WEEKS‼️
-
Coach: @_cutz_

12 DAYS OUT 💨
-
You know what they say, time flies when you’re having fun… and we’re just getting started! Time to finish this one strong 💪🏽
-
@_cutz_ 🔪

Peak week starts tomorrow‼️
-
8 days out today and I feel as if everything is falling into place. Made some posing adjustments today with @b_laurent_fit_ifbbpro , 5 more workouts, 4 more cardio sessions and it’s GAME TIME💪🏽
-
Coach: @_cutz_ 🔪

Happy 4th AND a happy 4 days out💪🏽🇺🇸
-
I love this country and I love what I do! Peak week is in full affect, time to execute coach’s plan, and really dig deep to finish this to the best of my ability. 
-
Excited for this peaking process as I believe this will be the best one yet with coach @_cutz_ in my corner. Almost time to fill out… See you soon Wisco 🧀 🍺

2023 MP OVERALL BREW CITY CHAMP 🥇 🏆 
-
Thank you to my family, friends, coach @_cutz_ and everyone else that supported me during this prep. I am grateful for you all, my loving girlfriend @madisen_dobbs , and everyone else in-between. Also, @shreddedcheddarproductions for putting on a great show once again! 
-
The work is far from over, time to improve these next 3 weeks, Sin city here we come. 🌴 🍹 
-
3 weeks out USA’s 🇺🇸
-
Coach: @_cutz_ 
Posing coach: @b_laurent_fit_ifbbpro

2 weeks, 4 days 🇺🇸
-
Enjoying the process and remembering these moments as I prepare for the biggest show of my life. I want to say thank you to everyone who congratulated me this past weekend, but that time is now in the past and the work must continue. Time to get better and bring my 100% 💪🏽
-
Coach: @_cutz_ 🔪
@musclecontest

Post workout updates from yesterday’s back training. 💪🏽
-
I received my feedback from the judges this past weekend and know what I need to work on to bring my best in 2.5 weeks. @_cutz_ had said we weren’t at our best yet and planned to bring me into Brew City at about 85-90%. 
-
Excited to make these improvements going into USA’s, and I am doing everything in my power to step on stage as an improved me. Back to work we go!
-
Coach: @_cutz_ 🔪
@musclecontest

2 weeks out from USA’s @musclecontest 🇺🇸
-
Things are slowly falling into place. Had a chance to book another posing session with @b_laurent_fit_ifbbpro to help bring me to my best, and honestly he is helping me tremendously. If you need help with posing this is your guy!
-
No matter what happens in 2 weeks, I know I have given this prep my all. Coach @_cutz_ has a plan, and I’m executing daily. Checking all the boxes I can control, and making sure I give it my 110%. Excited is an understatement for USA’s and lots of memories will be made. Let’s finish strong! 💪🏽

Almost reaching the week and a half out mark 🏁 
-
Updates taken yesterday post arms. Energy is hitting an all time low, but I made a promise to myself to bring my best and to do whatever it takes to reach that goal. Good, better, best never let it rest until you’re good is better and you’re better is best!! So here we are, let’s continue to improve and get better! 1 week, 6 days. 💯💪🏽

“It’s not the size of the dog in the fight, it’s the size of the fight in the dog.” 
-
9 days out 🔥 
@musclecontest 🇺🇸
Coach: @_cutz_ 🔪

IT’S PEAK WEEK 🔥
-
7 days out from NPC USA’S
@musclecontest 🇺🇸
-
The suffering & hard work is coming to an end, the fill out process is near, and coach @_cutz_ seems to be happy with the progress we have made so far.
-
I’m grateful & excited for this opportunity, and I am checking all my boxes to bring my absolute best this week. Let’s finish what we started! #jobnotfinished

5 days out from NPC USA’s @musclecontest 🇺🇸
-
The suffering, the hard work, the grit, blood, sweat, and tears that I have given this prep will make it my best one yet. Each year I set a goal to beat my previous package, and in a short 5 days I will showcase the work I have put in to do so.
-
With that said, the work is almost over, but it must continue as I prepare for battle. I have never pushed myself to this limit, mentally or physically, and at the end of the day I can look back and say, “I did this.”
-
5 days to make my dream a reality. We don’t stop here 💯
-
@_cutz_ 🔪

The worse you feel, the better you look. Let’s get alien shredded 👽
-
4 days out NPC USA’s @musclecontest 🇺🇸
-
@_cutz_ 🔪

ONE DAY OUT‼️
-
All checked in yesterday, #440 it’s all going down tomorrow. 💪🏽
-
I want to say thank you to everyone who has reached out to me so far, supported me, and believed in me this prep. All the hard work is done, countless hours of cardio, training, and not a meal missed this prep. It all comes down to tomorrow.
-
Tune in to @musclecontest ‘s page for live coverage and posts on the show. I’m excited for this one guys, let’s make this dream a reality. Love you all. 🙏🏽
-
Coach: @_cutz_ 🔪
Posing coach: @b_laurent_fit_ifbbpro 💪🏽

NPC USA’s pre judging by is a wrap! 
@musclecontest 🇺🇸
-
Things don’t always go your way, and today they certainly didn’t go the way as planned for myself. Am I upset? Not at all! I know I did everything in my power to bring my best look to date, and nobody can take that away from me. 
-
With that said, I want to say thank you to my family, my loving girlfriend , and of course the man behind my physique coach @_cutz_ 🔪
-
I love you all and have appreciated the support this prep, it truly means the world to me and keeps me goin. Back to the drawing board, and time to finish tonight at finals. I love bodybuilding 💪🏽
-
Huge shout out to @w_wittmannphoto for this amazing shot! I can’t wait to see the rest my man! Also, a huge shout out to @cheat_the_beach_tanning ☀️ thank you for everything!
-
Coach: @_cutz_ 
Posing coach: @b_laurent_fit_ifbbpro

After a much needed weekend post show, I got to spend it with my favorite person in the world. 
🌎 
-
This one goes out to my number one supporter, my best friend, and the one girl that is shaping me in becoming the man I am today. @madisen_dobbs 💕
-
For those of you who don’t know, Madi and I both compete together and prepped together the past 20+ weeks. Through thick and thin this girl and I have went through hell and back the last few months. I watched madi bust her ass in prep, fight battles with her thyroid, and never once did you see her complain or talk about it on IG. She fought, and she fought HARD. We moved into a new home together ON peak week 3.5 weeks ago, competed, worked two jobs each between us both,  made sacrifices, lots of sacrifices, stepped away from family and friends, and the list can just go on and on right? 
-
You can’t always control the way life goes, but you can always control what YOU and your partner can control to make sure success is always the end victory, and I always win with you no matter what babe. We both have grown so much these past few months together, and I am so beyond proud to say you are simply the best girl any man could ever ask for. 
-
Your resilience, passion, work ethic, and love for me is like no other. You not only complete me but, but complete my life with you in it, and make life easy. I love you so much, and I forever will remember these moments with you. Thank you for being my number 1 always. Madisen Taylor, none of this would have been possible without you, you are my ride or die, and I am damn glad to say that is true. I love you ❤️

One of my favorite things about competing is enjoying my time before and after the show with my friends and family.
-
Sharing these moments with you guys will be a memory that will last a life time, and I’m so glad I was able to make the most of it with my people. 💪🏽❤️
-
If we didn’t get a picture together this weekend, you all know who you are, and with that said thank you for being able to make this weekend a great one. I live for this 💪🏽
-
I also want to take the time to say thank you to my coach @_cutz_ for bringing me in the best we could, and to the rest of the cutz guys that made this even more special for me. Til’ next time… #cutzsistency 🔪

“Gentleman face the curtain.” 😈
-
Thank you @w_wittmannphoto for this amazing shot! So pleased with how they turned out and I can’t wait to share them all with you guys. 💪🏽

This one guys out to the 🐐,the man, the legend, and the one behind my physique. Coach @_cutz_ 🔪
-
Although my goal was not reached of obtaining my pro card, we brought my best look to date, and that right there is a W. Bodybuilding is an individualized sport, and improvement from show to show is exactly how my goal will be reached next year. We collected data, we know what we need to bring next time, and we will be back better than ever next year. I also want to thank all of the guys on the team, the support from each of you is like no other and it’s truly special to be apart of. This one is for you coach! 
-
@musclecontest 🇺🇸

Probably my favorite look to date. This was the night before the show where I carbed on 600+ carbs, and a burger / fry meal to end the night. 🍔 🍟 
-
This prep taught me a lot about myself. Mental and physical toughness I didn’t know I had, strength I didn’t know I had, moments where I didn’t think I had it in me, but I did, and I never gave up.
-
The beauty of bodybuilding is that nobody can do the work for you, but you certainly can do it for yourself. My goal has changed… it’s not chasing the pro card. It’s chasing the pro level physique. Back to work we go. 💪🏽
Official stage shots 2023 NPC USA Championships @musclecontest 🇺🇸

3 hours out before stage time at NPC USA’s. @musclecontest 🇺🇸
-
Thank you @jaygmno & @jordan__houghton for this dope shot before pre-judging! I’m so excited to grow this off season and make the improvements needed to bring in a better me. Let’s run it back 💪🏽
-
@_cutz_ 🔪

This was a very hard post for me to make, but something I felt needed to be done. Full transparency here of my 25 week prep from point A, to B. 
-
I started back with @_cutz_ last year in December, and I will never ever look back. During the course of this time I busted my ass to reach a new physique I didn’t even know I was capable of. You can do anything you set your mind to and I was determined to bring the best version of myself once I stepped on that stage for each contest I prepared for this year. 
-
Never give up on your dreams, it won’t come easy, mine still hasn’t been reached but that’s the best part about bodybuilding, it’s not the destination, it’s the journey… and the time is NOW‼️💪🏽
-
Coach: @_cutz_ 🔪
Posing coach: @b_laurent_fit_ifbbpro

2 weeks post show physique check ✅ 
-
Making sure to hold myself accountable in this rebound phase, really happy with where we are at right now. Up 5lbs from show day weight, Staying on track, eating my 6 meals coach @_cutz_ provides me with on our reverse diet and trying my best to set myself up for success this upcoming off season. 💪🏽 
-
Staying tight! 🔪
Coach: @_cutz_ 
Posing coach: @b_laurent_fit_ifbbpro

Babe said “make an ONLY FANS” But you’re the only fan I will ever need 😏😘
-
On a serious note, this weekend was a blast and it feels so good to have some normalcy back in my life with my lady, friends, and family. Love you all and thanks to everyone that came to our house warming party!

Cheers to 26 years young! 🥂
-
I am very thankful and fortunate to do what I love, have the right people in my corner, and have a loving family / friends that support me. You all are the best and made my year great, but let’s make 26 even better and a year of success. 
-
Special shout out to my honey for doing all you do for me. I love you! 
-
Now let’s make 26 great 😎

Prep files 🔪
-
Reaching new heights in life whether it’s with bodybuilding, work related, or exceeding personal growth all comes with being uncomfortable to achieve that goal. 
-
One thing I thank bodybuilding for is letting me get uncomfortable when trying to achieve a new level in life, and here… I was certainly uncomfortable but in the best condition I have ever been in. Moral of the story, don’t be afraid to get uncomfortable when unlocking new levels. 💯

We were hittin’ @_cutz_ 🔥
-
2 days out here from NPC USA’s. This upcoming off season will be huge for me. As I mature as a person and as a bodybuilder, I am in no rush to get back on stage and want to come back at my best. Luckily I have the best people in my corner to do so. 
-
Good luck to all my guys competing this weekend at North Americans!

My favorite look to date. One day post show. 💪🏽
-
I am beyond excited to grow this off season and take my physique to another level. My workouts are getting better each week now that I am a month and a half post show and my motivation is coming back to improve and grow upon this look. I love bodybuilding. Let’s work. 😤

Fun fact: I remember taking this video a week out from @shreddedcheddarproductions, and didn’t like the way that I looked. I remember people telling me I was ready, saying I was peeled, but man I didn’t see what they saw.
-
Prep can play some serious mind games on you, but that’s why I have the best coach and support system I could ever ask for! Coach @_cutz_ established I need a solid 10lbs of tissue before stepping back on stage so I have my work cut out for me this off season but with that said I’m really excited to bring an improved me next time I touch that stage. 
-
Health phase is going well, and labs have been scheduled. Almost time to push food and grow.💪🏽

PEAK WEEK VIBES😤
-
A lil TBT action one week out from show #1 this year. 
I have to say … I have scored touchdowns, I’ve made buckets, I’ve scored goals, and I’ve made assists… but nothing giving me more fulfillment and gratification than bodybuilding. I love this shit. 💯
Control what you can control 🤌🏽

I love this. 
-
Back in the groove of things to make this off season as successful as possible. Watching the outcome of @legionsportsfest fired me up, and with the Olympia around the corner I always get a blast of motivation by watching the top competitors. This is what I love to do!

Olympia weekend always fires me up 🔥 
-
Here are a few clips I use as a reminder to myself of what I am capable of achieving. The goal is clear, but the ride ahead is what makes this journey and bodybuilding fun. 💪🏽
On the weekends we like to hit up different gyms! Trained delts + tris tonight. Thanks for having us @gvl_fitness , awesome atmosphere & love the old school vibe…will def be back 💪
Felt full here, might delete later. 🤷🏼‍♂️💪🏽
